{"tid":628142,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以收胸收腹","createTime":"2018-04-13T14:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:40:16.000Z","uid":119012,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3045e34e3c4dc9c76eef484fc4ec628ca73dadb4","tid":628142,"uid":119012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"我20歲 小學時好少運動又食肉獸<br />\n搞到成個肥仔<br />\n之後決定做多運動 玩過籃球田徑(校隊)<br />\n少左食高脂嘅食物<br />\n依然係肥仔但叫做好左啲<br />\n依家番大專少左時間運動<br />\n又變番個肥仔<br />\n主要肥係肚腩(一條車肽)同胸口<br />\n但胸同肚腩之間果少少就唔肥<br />\n想問下做掌上壓同平衡支撐收唔收呢2個位"},{"pid":"eae07f6ca2e0e0b5f438eb6dccd0361e61e5ea9e","tid":628142,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"減脂無得淨係減一部分<br />\n重量訓練同帶氧運動都要做<br />\n連登Gym撚都唔少，可以問吓"},{"pid":"23819944344da55ce06c8214ee8ad59efbb99c22","tid":628142,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"做重訓同HITT"},{"pid":"70bee9d1cb68f547c7f34a380888ed089c2517b7","tid":628142,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"有人會胸同肚中間都肥埋？"},{"pid":"d2de9badfc9dae08d61ff50cca943fa58b2fc003","tid":628142,"uid":172020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70bee9d1cb68f547c7f34a380888ed089c2517b7","tid":628142,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"有人會胸同肚中間都肥埋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"我都係"},{"pid":"9e9709109c33bbcc333cf51d7538c69009d15b09","tid":628142,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bf18ad1d2300e518be0fc7710995c9742585aeb","tid":628142,"uid":119012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70bee9d1cb68f547c7f34a380888ed089c2517b7","tid":628142,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"有人會胸同肚中間都肥埋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"一舊過或3節棍<br />\n我小學係咁<br />\n係企直都3舊dur落黎"},{"pid":"e1223e31c68e24e5cdde03d72e2090477dca9ef1","tid":628142,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"減肥係全身性，訓練只係操肌肉，唔會影響果個位脂肪含量，肚係最後先瘦嘅地方，因為身體會保留脂肪保護內臟。<br />\n<br />\n標準答案係做全身性運動，重訓，有氧，進階先到HIIT。你唔戒口做乜都哂氣。"},{"pid":"aaec6e31cd90503478ed29dc54ee36786d15d6c0","tid":628142,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e9709109c33bbcc333cf51d7538c69009d15b09","tid":628142,"uid":74262,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"做小量帶氧當cross training 幾好"}]}